All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
public class HelpPanel
extends RightPanel

Class HelpPanel has the specific size of 480 x 480 pixel and shows a help text. The possible action to a HelpPanel is to close it by clicking a button. To get this event, you have to register an ActionListener.

Version:
1.0
